instructions: place the plate on the center of the tablecloth
put the fork on the left side of the plate
place the dinner knife on the right side of the plate
put the salad fork on the left side of the dinner fork
put the salad knife on the right side of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon on the right side of the salad knife
put the dessert spoon above the dinner plate with the end of the spoon facing the diner knife
put the desert fork directly under the desert spoon facing the opposite way
place the bread plate above the salad fork
place the butter knife horizontal on the bread plate with the tip facing away
place the water glass above the diner knife
place the napkin in the center of the plate sitting up
